{"tid":1493643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[何妖仆街未？]律師會將以投訴人身份接手針對何君堯的投訴","createTime":"2019-08-21T10:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:55:19.000Z","uid":267024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea36bd31da0443f262c1743866ea7ba65c719ce","tid":1493643,"uid":267024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"朋友早排send左email去香港律師會投訴何妖勾結黑幫，損害律師專業名譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日收到咁既回覆:<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n調查委員會已審查此個案並議決如下：<br />\n<br />\nThe Law Society will take up the complaints against Mr. Ho Kwan Yiu referred by members of the public (&ldquo;Informants&rdquo;) as complainant.  As all conduct investigation is confidential, the Informants will not be informed of the progress or result of the investigation.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">律師會將以投訴人的身份接手由公眾人士（&ldquo;舉報人士&rdquo;）提出的針對何君堯律師的投訴，由於所有專業操守調查均屬保密，舉報人士將不會被告知調查的進展情況或結果。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n=======<br />\n則係話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港律師會接力投訴何君堯</span></span>？<br />\n但又<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔通知審訊過程同結果</span>係咩玩法？<br />\n收到依個回覆 係應該開心定唔開心..<br />\n有無人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f97e16f3f2da0b120113c95ab5faf9217d7dc26","tid":1493643,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea36bd31da0443f262c1743866ea7ba65c719ce","tid":1493643,"uid":267024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"朋友早排send左email去香港律師會投訴何妖勾結黑幫，損害律師專業名譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日收到咁既回覆:<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n調查委員會已審查此個案並議決如下：<br />\n<br />\nThe Law Society will take up the complaints against Mr. Ho Kwan Yiu referred by members of the public (&ldquo;Informants&rdquo;) as complainant.  As all conduct investigation is confidential, the Informants will not be informed of the progress or result of the investigation.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">律師會將以投訴人的身份接手由公眾人士（&ldquo;舉報人士&rdquo;）提出的針對何君堯律師的投訴，由於所有專業操守調查均屬保密，舉報人士將不會被告知調查的進展情況或結果。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n=======<br />\n則係話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港律師會接力投訴何君堯</span></span>？<br />\n但又<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔通知審訊過程同結果</span>係咩玩法？<br />\n收到依個回覆 係應該開心定唔開心..<br />\n有無人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1aa393f4f9a70c6c7980350496cb3ea5aaaea6c","tid":1493643,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4868c88454c69d29c4fedd4ba8ce2ac294b469c","tid":1493643,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ca4385334f5132684399e3ffc5b7e9ac4904ad","tid":1493643,"uid":251206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"何妖一定要攪，不過估計無用，但一畀立法會最小要踢走佢，睇下仲有無得做西環契仔"},{"pid":"04932d64462cce035e4b38476987226c6ab3e3c5","tid":1493643,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"take over左你個投訴，有無/有咩result 你都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n某程度即係做唔做野都唔知"},{"pid":"ca99ac7af7e069065c0677441023e45900ff73d0","tid":1493643,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5946f49e3cdce65bdb0fa2ada0eba97bb8f77f1d","tid":1493643,"uid":267024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2692a6cdae700c7f5bcb8b1da73de71c8c4bc1fa","tid":1493643,"uid":267024,"like":0,"dislik